Preview

I've added two new sections to the landing page: a "Production Ready" section that showcases Neptuno's production architecture with an animated visualization, and an SDK section that demonstrates the TypeScript SDK with interactive code examples. The Production Ready section highlights Neptuno's dockerized architecture with nginx, backend/frontend containers, and database replicas, while the SDK section shows how developers can quickly implement authentication, gamification, and event tracking features. Both sections maintain the modern design aesthetic and complement the existing content.

